des: Daily Moment takes 5 minutes out of your day for some me time. With Motivational Quotes, 30-90 second meditation time, 3 x Affirmations, Gratitudes and Visualisation of your day ahead; you'll be feeling positive and ready for the day ahead. Follow @DailyMomentApp on Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest and YouTube for a regular boost of positivity.
